snippet.textDisplay:
Thank you Casey!! THANK U SO MUCH FOR THIS!!! I will be 41 this May... been with my girl 13 years. 2 kids. And recently disabled from major medical issues. The 2020 new year really starting throwing me down the tubes of depression dwelling on how much of my life has been wasted. But this really put things into perspective for me. I'm not one to make bullshit new year resolutions. I am however one who made some new LIFE CHANGES. Im not wasting another day of this precious life. Regardless of how far gone I am. Thanks Again Casey!! From a fellow NYer...
But from the other end of the state. Plattsburgh NY.
